caption.p: Active antioxidant, antidiabetic, and neuroprotective compounds identified in the fruits essential oil of Elaeagnus umbellata Thunb. via GC-MS [( a) Octadecanoic acid, ( b) Cis-cis-9,12-Octadecadienoic acid (Linoleic acid), ( c) α-linolenic, ( d) 3,7,11,15-Tetramethyl-2-hexadecen-1-ol (Phytol), ( e) Humulene Epoxide, ( f) 2-Methoxy-4-vinylphenol ( p-Vinylguaiacol), ( g) (+)-Ascorbic acid 2,6-dihexadecanoate, ( h) Octadecanoic acid (Steric acid) ( i) Caryophyllene, ( j) (−)Caryophyllene oxide, ( k) Decanoic acid]
